Description: Feature Ordering by integrated R square Dependence (FORD) is a variable selection algorithm based on the new measure dependence: Integrated R2 dependence coefficent (IRDEC). For more information, see the paper: Azadkia and Roudaki (2025),"A NEW MEASURE OF DEPENDENCE: INTEGRATED R2" <arXiv:???>.
